title: WEDNESDAY 3/10 - Franchise tag deadline
itunes:title: WEDNESDAY 3/10 - Franchise tag deadline
description:
Tuesday was franchise tag deadline day. The Super Bowl Champions Buccaneers making some moves (0:09) to lock up a couple key pieces. The Giants tagging Leonard Williams (0:52) while head coach Joe Judge talked about the future of Daniel Jones in the Big Apple (1:04). Wide Receiver Allen Robinson (2:02) tagged in Chicago, while a pair of NFC North opponents choosing to let some star players test the free agent market (2:02). Plus, the Ravens looking to extend quarterback Lamar Jackson (2:39)
